---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
import RandomColor from '../components/RandomColor.astro';
import Button from '../components/Button.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Services">
  <section>
    <h1>
      Services for <RandomColor>automation</RandomColor>, internal tools, dashboards, and spreadsheet-heavy operations
    </h1>
    <p>
      I help startups, agencies, and remote teams reduce manual work, improve reporting, and build practical internal systems without needing a full-time engineer.
    </p>
  </section>

  <section>
    <h2>1. Fractional automation support</h2>
    <p>
      Best for teams that need ongoing help improving workflows, connecting systems, and removing repetitive operational work.
    </p>
    <ul>
      <li>Python scripts and backend automations</li>
      <li>API integrations and data sync workflows</li>
      <li>scheduled reporting and recurring ops improvements</li>
      <li>part-time support for internal systems</li>
    </ul>
  </section>

  <section>
    <h2>2. Internal dashboards & reporting systems</h2>
    <p>
      Best for businesses that rely on spreadsheets or manual reporting and need clearer visibility into their operations.
    </p>
    <ul>
      <li>dashboards for founders, operators, and teams</li>
      <li>reporting pipelines and structured data flows</li>
      <li>Google Sheets / Excel based reporting improvements</li>
      <li>custom visualisation and lightweight analytics tooling</li>
    </ul>
  </section>

  <section>
    <h2>3. Spreadsheet-to-system upgrades</h2>
    <p>
      Best for teams that have outgrown manual spreadsheet workflows but are not ready for a large rebuild.
    </p>
    <ul>
      <li>Excel and Google Sheets workflow redesign</li>
      <li>Apps Script, VBA, Python, and API-based enhancements</li>
      <li>better data structure, validation, and automation</li>
      <li>custom interfaces and lightweight internal apps around existing workflows</li>
    </ul>
  </section>

  <section>
    <h2>Typical client fit</h2>
    <p>
      I’m a strong fit for SaaS startups, agencies, and data-heavy businesses that want practical technical help with operations, reporting, and internal tooling.
    </p>
    <p>
      If your team is still doing too much manual work in spreadsheets, stitching together reports by hand, or juggling disconnected systems, that is usually where I can help the most.
    </p>
  </section>

  <section>
    <h2>Engagement style</h2>
    <p>
      I’m available for part-time support, hourly work, retainers, or clearly scoped projects. I work well with async-friendly remote teams and can collaborate through calls when needed.
    </p>
    <p style="text-align: center; margin-top: 1.25rem;">
      <Button href="/about">Discuss your workflow or reporting problem →</Button>
    </p>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
